data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2,864 square foot Fulton-built Craftsman Bungalow styled home. Boasting 4+ bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this spacious residence includes a large loft, a 3-car garage, and a pebble-textured pool with three soothing waterfalls. The outdoor BBQ kitchen island setup and landscaped grassy backyard creates the perfect setting for entertaining and relaxation. Step inside to discover an open concept living space that features a must-see kitchen makeover, complete with a continent-sized granite island/bar, upgraded staggered cabinets, royal crown trim, and an exotic stone backsplash. Stainless steel appliances include a gas oven/range and microwave, making this kitchen a dream for any chef. This home is thoughtfully appointed with two newer air conditioning units.
